    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "Older fair-condition example that presents as a solid, usable driver but not a show car. Expect visible cosmetic wear, age-related blemishes, and an interior that shows regular use, though it remains functional and serviceable. It runs and drives as it should for this level, making it a reasonable option for someone looking for an entry-level classic or weekend cruiser without paying top-tier money. An honest car for a buyer who values usability over perfection.",
