    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Affordable, straightforward, and priced to move, this vehicle is a practical choice for anyone seeking low-cost transportation without unnecessary extras. It shows its age cosmetically, but offers solid value for a budget-minded buyer, commuter, or first-time driver looking for an economical way to get on the road. A smart opportunity to own a vehicle at an accessible price point.",
