      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 11
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Honest little car that\u2019s ready for someone who wants affordable wheels and doesn\u2019t mind a bit of TLC. It\u2019s not perfect, but it\u2019s a great budget-friendly option for a runabout, first car, or weekend project. If you\u2019re after something straightforward, usable, and priced with real-world value in mind, this one could be a smart buy.",
      "price": 6950.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 11
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid project car with great bones and a strong enthusiast vibe. The powertrain pulls well, the chassis feels planted, and it has the kind of mechanical honesty that makes it a great candidate for someone who wants an affordable driver to sort and enjoy. Shows wear consistent with age and use, but it\u2019s complete, presentable from a distance, and has plenty of upside for a hands-on owner. If you\u2019re looking for a budget-friendly platform with real character and room to improve, this one is worth a look.",
      "price": 6950.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 11
    },
    {
